<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Collinearity_of_points_whose_pairwise_distances_are_given">Collinearity of points whose pairwise distances are given</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Collinearity&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Collinearity of points whose pairwise distances are given"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
